## Recently Completed

- **TennisRecord integration**: Opponent scouting, player ratings, head-to-head detection
- **AI league commentary**: Pre-match hype + post-match recap emails with scouting data
- **Player form summaries**: AI one-liner on player profiles, auto-updated on score submission
